generate_target_weight_position:
1. get the risk data on the last day(risk data can be created by <qlib.model.riskmodel.structured.StructuredCovEstimator>
2. use the latest score
3. get the current weight
4. get bench weight (mind here D.instrument is used, so the strategy is not fully decoupled)
5. delete the blacklist
6. calculate the best weight using self.optimizer (EnhancedIndexingOptimizer)
7. submit the orders
